summary: A ENB preset for an enhancement of the graphics of the game.
descriptionHtml:
[img]http://image.noelshack.com/fichiers/2014/06/1391726341-dark1.jpg[/img]

Dark Forest in a ENB preset for an enhancement of the graphics of the game.

--- Description ---

Discover a world between darkness and light. The humidity wet you and hot air touch your face.
Your horse is just behind you, waiting for more adventures. Your sword in the hand, you are the Dovahkiin.

--- Installation ---

1. Install WinRar : http://www.clubic.com/telecharger-fiche9632-winrar.html
2. Download the file - On the file category
3. Open it with WinRar and drag the extract the content to yout skyrim folder
4. Enjoy

--- Compatibility ---

Compatible with every lighting mods.
Need a good computer.
Can be mixed with others ENB.
Works with every camera and graphics mods.
Don't install Post-Process Effects Addon for ENB.

--- Credits ---

Enb configuration made by MrBrenan
Enb series made by Boris Voronstof

--- Recommended ---

On the night or on a dungeon, the dark is really hard, I recommended to you to download the wearable lantern mod : http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/17416/ .



Enjoy !!!
And give me your impression !
author: MrBrenan
